Oral anticoagulants for prevention of stroke in atrial fibrillation: systematic 
review, network meta-analysis, and cost effectiveness analysis.

López-López JA(1), Sterne JAC(2)(3), Thom HHZ(1), Higgins JPT(1)(3), Hingorani 
AD(4), Okoli GN(1), Davies PA(1)(5), Bodalia PN(6)(7), Bryden PA(1), Welton 
