Advancing research in medicine and technology has benefitted the mankind 
immensely with its contribution toward an improved life quality and increased 
life expectancy. The inability of a human body to autoregenerate has resulted in 
an increased demand for newer and healthier tissues and organs. Therefore, the 
restoration of naturally replicated tissue components has become a subject of 
