Effectiveness of support groups to improve the quality of life of people with 
idiopathic pulmonary fibrosis a pre-post test pilot study.

Magnani D(1), Lenoci G, Balduzzi S, Artioli G, Ferri P.

Author information:
(1)University of Modena and Reggio Emilia. paola.ferri@unimore.it.

BACKGROUND AND AIM OF THE WORK: Idiopathic Pulmonary Fibrosis (IPF) is an 
interstitial lung disease, which progressively leads to severe disability and 
